34b60a20757eeca6554b34908","tid":131574,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:22:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去死啦大學毒sci on99</blockquote><br />\n好大怨氣喎巴打 點解咁講嘅 <br />\nScience都幾好玩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有家底真好</blockquote><br />\n讀得science家底都好架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔洗養家就無問題"},{"pid":"9c311b4fb1d7a79aaf1daea2d0382f89eaed6313","tid":131574,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:23:17.000Z","msg":"herman yeung個youtube channel有教dse chem 仲教得勁好 <br />\n樓主可以去睇下"},{"pid":"9fc939d6bb9f92883303ffd29c55819a714d13cf","tid":131574,"uid":81105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:24:39.000Z","msg":"Periodic table <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7dfabacf1c3afb49a6281fa4db3c862b1fd802","tid":131574,"uid":36789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:31:07.000Z","msg":"睇下GCSE教科書先(好過DSE)<br />\n<br />\n睇完再睇GCE"},{"pid":"fdef642416be212f658a22af5b54d141ac9c9882","tid":131574,"uid":80580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:37:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主幾大？有無讀physics? 我覺得Chem 由electron 入手較好，可以先了解下electronic configuration個啲野，Lewis structure ，想學深啲可以接觸下少少quantum野。不過中學普遍由metal 開始教，但我覺得唔明箇中原理又背得好無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常人睇到quantum mechanic就想死<br />\n睇到hybridization仲有興趣 我話你叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95eae2d6669ac5071f0a6d980512195c2b47385","tid":131574,"uid":20364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T09:57:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主幾大？有無讀physics? 我覺得Chem 由electron 入手較好，可以先了解下electronic configuration個啲野，Lewis structure ，想學深啲可以接觸下少少quantum野。不過中學普遍由metal 開始教，但我覺得唔明箇中原理又背得好無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常人睇到quantum mechanic就想死<br />\n睇到hybridization仲有興趣 我話你叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以就叫樓主睇Lewis structure，dot and cross diagram比較簡單嘅容易上手啲<br />\n而quantum 就唔係quantum mechanics啦當然......講緊係physics 個種energy level （中學physics學嘅atomic world）所以想問下樓主有無讀physics, 因為atomic world 同Chem 都好大關連下"},{"pid":"772b57e3fc6184f6312ed5e5bfe9cd7aee7a0b7d","tid":131574,"uid":5750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:12:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27ad9fa5f94ec22e1a37306bb011c4b94f853889","tid":131574,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T12:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主幾大？有無讀physics? 我覺得Chem 由electron 入手較好，可以先了解下electronic configuration個啲野，Lewis structure ，想學深啲可以接觸下少少quantum野。不過中學普遍由metal 開始教，但我覺得唔明箇中原理又背得好無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常人睇到quantum mechanic就想死<br />\n睇到hybridization仲有興趣 我話你叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以就叫樓主睇Lewis structure，dot and cross diagram比較簡單嘅容易上手啲<br />\n而quantum 就唔係quantum mechanics啦當然......講緊係physics 個種energy level （中學physics學嘅atomic world）所以想問下樓主有無讀physics, 因為atomic world 同Chem 都好大關連下</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講多d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c28d39e4a29c878fc0f22e5f0ab12f3e6b3c54c","tid":131574,"uid":47430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T12:59:11.000Z","msg":"背熟個periodic table就係入門"},{"pid":"13bbea6aed945efb900a46f61113ab7fbdda347c","tid":131574,"uid":80580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:01:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主幾大？有無讀physics? 我覺得Chem 由electron 入手較好，可以先了解下electronic configuration個啲野，Lewis structure ，想學深啲可以接觸下少少quantum野。不過中學普遍由metal 開始教，但我覺得唔明箇中原理又背得好無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常人睇到quantum mechanic就想死<br />\n睇到hybridization仲有興趣 我話你叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以就叫樓主睇Lewis structure，dot and cross diagram比較簡單嘅容易上手啲<br />\n而quantum 就唔係quantum mechanics啦當然......講緊係physics 個種energy level （中學physics學嘅atomic world）所以想問下樓主有無讀physics, 因為atomic world 同Chem 都好大關連下</blockquote><br />\n唔知physics既atomic world係咩 無讀physics   我一開始學完Bohr model 就quantum mechanics<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a138beea0eb9780a2e92c51baecb90c8f6cad9f","tid":131574,"uid":62675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:50:41.000Z","msg":"唔好讀哂銀時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130126be7726c0194648a203fda972f4be2a4531","tid":131574,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:21:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74e8cc93f12d83443df16717fbbe5493caeae644","tid":131574,"uid":81671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:28:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想唔想要dse chem書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我有齊 有興趣要既平賣比你 (唔想當廢紙回收賣)</blockquote><br />\nbro，有無bio?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}